text: Connect With PlantSulin Customer Success Team PlantSulin are here to help you reach your health goals! If you have any questions, concerns or wish to provide feedback, please contact us with the information below. Contacting Support Phone 1-866-450-0610 (7AM to 9PM /7 Days a week) Email support@getplantsulin.com PlantSulin team works around the clock to provide the best customer support possible. If you contact us by phone or chat, you should get a response from a live agent within a few minutes. If you contact us by email, expect a response within 24 hours or less.
